text you from her phone

19:03.852 --> 19:06.270
and just wait for you to come runnin'.
But, hey...

19:06.271 --> 19:07.689
fuckin' Christmas.

19:15.071 --> 19:16.406
Nice one.

19:17.448 --> 19:19.950
But I don't break easy no more.

19:19.951 --> 19:21.618
Not like Mallory.

19:21.619 --> 19:23.412
You're a right tough lad, ain't ya?

19:23.413 --> 19:26.249
Killing an old lady,
then fucking off to Russia.

19:27.834 --> 19:29.711
Zoe was right about you.

19:31.004 --> 19:33.131
Maybe I should just put you
out of your misery.

19:35.091 --> 19:36.092
You could.

19:37.093 --> 19:38.176
But you won't.

19:38.177 --> 19:40.053
- And why is that?
- 'Cause...

19:40.054 --> 19:42.973
we both loved the same woman...

19:42.974 --> 19:45.476
and we both hate the same cunt.

19:48.229 --> 19:51.315
Look, mate,
you can be as pissy with me as you like,

19:51.316 --> 19:53.609
but we both know

19:53.610 --> 19:55.486
I ain't the bad guy here.

19:56.905 --> 19:58.197
Not really.

19:59.574 --> 20:00.866
I just need us

20:00.867 --> 20:02.243
to have a proper chat.

20:03.578 --> 20:04.996
That's all.

20:10.668 --> 20:11.835
Homelander?

20:11.836 --> 20:13.378
Up here.

20:13.379 --> 20:14.380
What do you--

20:16.007 --> 20:17.800
What in the fuck?

20:20.261 --> 20:22.054
- Is that milk?
- Better.

20:22.055 --> 20:24.681
Breastmilk.
From the NICU at Mount Sinai.

20:24.682 --> 20:27.976
So, what, you asked me up here
so I could watch you swim in tit-jizz?

20:27.977 --> 20:29.686
I want to give you another chance.

20:29.687 --> 20:31.688
You want to give me another chance?

20:31.689 --> 20:33.774
Yes. Help me find that V1.

20:33.775 --> 20:36.401
