with a handful of razors.

20:36.402 --> 20:40.530
Besides, Cleopatra Jones said
there's no V1 to find.

20:40.531 --> 20:42.533
Oh, there most certainly is.

20:43.743 --> 20:45.870
And I am going to find it.

20:46.913 --> 20:48.038
Yeah? What makes you so sure?

20:48.039 --> 20:49.624
An angel told me.

20:50.875 --> 20:52.293
It's my destiny.

20:53.044 --> 20:54.670
Just when I thought there was a ceiling

20:54.671 --> 20:56.463
to how fucking weird you could get.

20:56.464 --> 20:59.132
Yes, yes. Make your jokes.

20:59.133 --> 21:01.135
You've been blessed with immortality...

21:02.136 --> 21:03.512
...and what have you done with it?

21:03.513 --> 21:06.306
Drink and fuck yourself numb.

21:06.307 --> 21:07.684
You...

21:09.435 --> 21:11.061
...you...

21:11.062 --> 21:12.647
are a disappointment.

21:15.650 --> 21:17.443
You see...

21:19.404 --> 21:23.031
...I am not gonna waste my immortality.

21:23.032 --> 21:25.617
I am gonna take what's rightfully mine.

21:25.618 --> 21:28.036
