if you want a seat at the table

21:28.037 --> 21:29.287
because you're my father.

21:29.288 --> 21:31.749
But with or without you...

21:32.750 --> 21:34.419
...a reckoning is coming.

21:36.879 --> 21:38.381
You know, all I see is a freak.

21:39.215 --> 21:41.884
A freak with a bushel of gray pubes.

21:43.553 --> 21:45.138
Try some Just for Men.

22:00.695 --> 22:02.571
What's Fort Harmony?

22:02.572 --> 22:03.822
I have no idea.

22:03.823 --> 22:04.865
It's all over these memos.

22:04.866 --> 22:05.907
What do they say?

22:05.908 --> 22:07.367
I don't know.

22:07.368 --> 22:09.661
The text is encrypted,
but I think I can crack it.

22:09.662 --> 22:10.662
You couldn't possibly.

22:10.663 --> 22:12.247
It's 1944.

22:12.248 --> 22:13.957
There's more processing power
in your toaster

22:13.958 --> 22:15.752
than there was
in the encryption tech back then.

22:16.627 --> 22:17.503
Gimme an hour.

22:20.048 --> 22:21.966
The fuck is that?

22:35.396 --> 22:36.772
Hey.

22:36.773 --> 22:38.940
Um, sorry... Just, uh...

22:38.941 --> 22:41.276
...you might wanna lighten up on that

22:41.277 --> 22:43.779
V-Bro Mango Thunder. That is...

22:43.780 --> 22:45.781
that is musky.

22:45.782 --> 22:47.699
My dad was
in the first campaign.

22:47.700 --> 22:49.910
"Vanish into Freshness."

22:49.911 --> 22:52.497
It just... smells like him, you know?

22:53.539 --> 22:54.957
I'm sorry about your dad.

22:55.625 --> 22:57.919
I-I lost mine too.

22:59.003 --> 23:00.003
I'm sorry to hear that.

23:00.004 --> 23:01.797
It's just... it's crazy, right?

23:01.798 --> 23:03.548
Walk around one day feeling fine,

23:03.549 --> 23:04.550
and then...

23:05.635 --> 23:08.136
...outta nowhere, the pain just hits you
like a truck, like...

23:08.137 --> 23:10.013
just takes the wind out of you.

23:10.014 --> 23:13.266
You guys are trying to take
down Homelander, right? Let me help.

23:13.267 --> 23:16.228
Look, Maverick, I-I don't think
that's such a good idea. It...

23:16.229 --> 23:17.562
It's really dangerous.

23:17.563 --> 23:20.023
I don't care. He fucking killed my dad.

23:20.024 --> 23:21.691
It's the only thing I can think about.

23:21.692 --> 23:23.693
I know that
you want this to mean something.

23:23.694 --> 23:25.780
But it's never gonna make sense.

23:26.906 --> 23:29.158
And the more that you try,
the less sense it'll make. It...

23:30.660 --> 23:32.244
Trust me.

23:32.245 --> 23:33.703
I know.

23:33.704 --> 23:35.163
What am I supposed to do?

23:35.164 --> 23:36.456
Honestly? Just...

23:36.457 --> 23:38.792
let go.

23:38.793 --> 23:40.794
Live your life. Be happy.

23:40.795 --> 23:42.546
Fall in love with someone.

23:42.547 --> 23:44.131
I do have a girlfriend.

23:44.132 --> 23:45.132
Really?

23:45.133 --> 23:46.842
Sloane.

23:46.843 --> 23:48.427
She's an alpaca.

23:51.097 --> 23:52.305
Cool. Just--

23:52.306 --> 23:55.475
Maybe think about what your dad would
want for you, and-and then

23:55.476 --> 23:56.726
do that.

23:56.727 --> 23:58.854
That's what I'm trying to do, anyway.

23:58.855 --> 24:00.772
-  Hughie?
- Um...

24:00.773 --> 24:04.151
Can I, um, can I just talk to you
for a quick second?

24:04.152 --> 24:05.153
Yeah.

24:08.656 --> 24:09.866
Stop.

24:15.705 --> 24:18.999
Another mention of Fort Harmony.
From 1963.

24:19.000 --> 24:20.709
Butcher has a scanner, no?

24:20.710 --> 24:22.043
He does.

24:22.044 --> 24:24.796
Maybe resolution is good enough
so we can make out some of the text.

24:24.797 --> 24:26.214
Okay.

24:26.215 --> 24:27.674
- Go with him.
-  Sounds good.

24:27.675 --> 24:30.720
I've been watching pornography
and I'd like to try out some cunnilingus.

24:35.224 --> 24:36.517
I don't understand.

24:37.810 --> 24:39.102
All you do

24:39.103 --> 24:40.353
is get him on the blower

24:40.354 --> 24:41.980
and tell him you wanna see him.

24:41.981 --> 24:44.859
When he rocks up,
you chuck the shit in his face...

24:45.902 --> 24:47.569
...and that'll be it.

24:47.570 --> 24:49.154
- Why me?
- 'Cause he won't leave

24:49.155 --> 24:51.323
the fortress of cuntitude
for anyone else.

24:51.324 --> 24:53.201
So this is what
you wanted to talk to me about.

24:54.243 --> 24:55.619
Killing my dad.

24:55.620 --> 24:57.037
Listen, mate--

24:57.038 --> 24:58.413
