24:58.414 --> 25:00.832
I ain't gonna treat you
like a kid no more. All right?

25:00.833 --> 25:03.627
You're done with that.
Homelander raped yer mum.

25:03.628 --> 25:04.920
He's gonna burn everything down,

25:04.921 --> 25:07.423
and you are the only one
who can stop him.

25:08.382 --> 25:09.883
Now...

25:09.884 --> 25:13.845
normally, I don't put no stock in
any of that bollocks about destiny,

25:13.846 --> 25:16.890
but if anyone's got one, it's you.

25:21.229 --> 25:22.772
I throw this virus at him...

25:23.773 --> 25:25.441
...what'll happen to me?

25:27.193 --> 25:28.569
You'll die.

25:32.114 --> 25:34.367
I'll be close by and we'll go together.

25:36.327 --> 25:37.286
Now...

25:39.455 --> 25:41.165
...I ain't gonna lie to you, this...

25:42.166 --> 25:45.085
...this is not what your mum wanted.

25:45.086 --> 25:46.629
But it's the only way.

25:48.339 --> 25:50.716
And it will be justice.

25:53.386 --> 25:55.554
You're asking me to kill myself?

25:58.307 --> 26:00.977
You wouldn't be the first lad
to throw his life away in a war...

26:02.395 --> 26:04.854
but you would be the first

26:04.855 --> 26:07.817
to save the world doin' it.

26:19.537 --> 26:21.122
I'll fetch us a pint.

26:29.588 --> 26:30.880
♪ Keep rollin',
rollin', rollin', rollin...

26:30.881 --> 26:33.174
I mean, no wonder
Soldier Boy's getting all this heat.

26:33.175 --> 26:34.926
He's a fucking nepo daddy.

26:34.927 --> 26:36.928
Like, he's not even that good-looking.

26:36.929 --> 26:40.016
Like, his hair's doing
most of the heavy lifting.

26:41.225 --> 26:44.311
Like, you shave his head,
