26:49.567 --> 26:51.318
Will you just tell me this?

26:51.319 --> 26:53.194
Homelander really didn't want me
to come along?

26:53.195 --> 26:54.612
He didn't, like...

26:54.613 --> 26:56.156
mention my name even once?

26:56.157 --> 26:58.950
♪ So back the fuck up
while we fuck this track up...

26:58.951 --> 27:01.244
Then why'd he ask them?

27:07.835 --> 27:09.210
Keep heading south.

27:09.211 --> 27:11.004
♪ Hands down, back up, back up ♪

27:11.005 --> 27:12.881
♪ Tell me what you gonna do now...

27:12.882 --> 27:15.551
So, like, what's your story?

27:16.469 --> 27:17.510
My story?

27:17.511 --> 27:18.595
Yeah.

27:18.596 --> 27:20.847
I was born
on a Sugarbush Maple Farm.

27:20.848 --> 27:24.100
One day when I was five, my parents died
in a tidal wave of molasses.

27:24.101 --> 27:25.560
Then I was raised by four geese

27:25.561 --> 27:27.062
and an agoraphobic fox in a crystal cave

27:27.063 --> 27:29.064
where they taught me
the ways of the soil and the salts,

27:29.065 --> 27:32.025
until Gerald-- that's the eldest goose--

27:32.026 --> 27:34.903
revealed to me that he's
the reincarnation of Robin Williams.

27:34.904 --> 27:37.197
And then he took me
on his egg-shaped spaceship

27:37.198 --> 27:40.284
to Ork, because Mork & Mindy
is a Netflix documentary.

27:41.786 --> 27:43.162
Orson married us.

27:44.663 --> 27:46.498
And the rest is history.

27:46.499 --> 27:47.791
♪ Back up, back up ♪

27:47.792 --> 27:49.209
♪ Tell me what you're gonna do now ♪

27:49.210 --> 27:51.127
♪ Breathe in, now breathe out,
hands up, now hands down...

27:51.128 --> 27:53.254
Homelander asked you to come along?

27:53.255 --> 27:55.131
♪ Keep rollin', rollin', rollin...

27:55.132 --> 27:56.466
Personally.

27:56.467 --> 27:58.927
♪ Rollin', rollin', rollin', rollin' ♪

27:58.928 --> 28:00.804
♪ Keep rollin',
rollin', rollin', rollin' ♪

28:00.805 --> 28:03.681
♪ Keep rollin', rollin', rollin',
rollin' ♪

28:06.018 --> 28:07.560
Merde.

28:07.561 --> 28:10.481
Cybertrucks are the Entourage of cars.

28:15.444 --> 28:17.905
A penny for your thoughts?

28:19.740 --> 28:21.741
