28:48.686 --> 28:50.812
Of course not.

28:50.813 --> 28:53.149
Which is why I will never have any.

28:58.988 --> 29:00.448
But, uh...

29:02.074 --> 29:03.659
...you want children?

29:05.828 --> 29:07.036
Three.

29:07.037 --> 29:09.080
Two girls and a boy.
A house by the water.

29:09.081 --> 29:10.498
And maybe a bernedoodle.

29:10.499 --> 29:12.167
Peace and quiet.

29:12.168 --> 29:13.543
After all this killing,

29:13.544 --> 29:15.295
I just want a place to call home.

29:37.359 --> 29:38.444
Here.

29:39.653 --> 29:41.946
Told 'er you were 30.

29:41.947 --> 29:44.532
Fuck the leather,

29:44.533 --> 29:45.617
fuck the lace,

29:45.618 --> 29:47.703
here's to the bird
who sits on yer face.

29:53.083 --> 29:54.542
Where'd you pick that up?

29:54.543 --> 29:55.919
Me old man.

29:55.920 --> 29:57.712
You two close?

29:57.713 --> 29:59.589
Nah, not really.

29:59.590 --> 30:02.592
He was a... a piss artist.

30:02.593 --> 30:05.845
Used to lose all his money
on the gee-gees.

30:05.846 --> 30:07.347
Uh-- horses.

30:07.348 --> 30:10.809
And then he'd come home, beat
the livin' daylights outta Len and me.

30:12.770 --> 30:14.604
And then, later,

30:14.605 --> 30:16.314
laugh about it with his mates.

30:16.315 --> 30:18.191
Yeah, he was a right cunt.

30:18.192 --> 30:19.692
Where is he now?

30:19.693 --> 30:21.819
Bottom of the Thames.

30:21.820 --> 30:23.864
I put him there, just the other day.

30:25.908 --> 30:27.408
Only wish I'd done it sooner.

30:27.409 --> 30:29.286
'Fore he caused more...

30:31.580 --> 30:32.998
...more damage.

30:35.668 --> 30:37.044
Butcher...

30:39.004 --> 30:40.714
Do you think that I could ever...

30:41.924 --> 30:43.675
That I might turn into my dad?

30:48.013 --> 30:49.515
I don't know.

30:54.436 --> 30:56.105
My mom...

30:56.855 --> 30:58.773
Aunt Grace...

30:58.774 --> 31:00.150
the others...

31:00.818 --> 31:03.319
All I do is hurt people.

31:03.320 --> 31:05.239
I can't be around anyone.

31:11.453 --> 31:14.038
Without us--

31:14.039 --> 31:15.874
without Supes--

31:17.209 --> 31:21.212
the world is a better, safer place.

31:27.303 --> 31:28.512
I'll do it.

31:40.065 --> 31:42.900
 ...following the mass
arrests of suspected Starlighters,

31:42.901 --> 31:44.611
protestors have taken to the streets

31:44.612 --> 31:48.448
and clashed violently
with superheroes and police alike...

31:48.449 --> 31:51.534
It's all so tediously predictable.

31:51.535 --> 31:54.495
Insurgency, counter-insurgency.

31:54.496 --> 31:56.539
Liberation, crackdown.

31:56.540 --> 31:59.250
Round and round she goes.

31:59.251 --> 32:03.046
Is now a good time to say I've always
found you super fucking creepy?

32:03.047 --> 32:04.047
Mm.

32:04.048 --> 32:06.591
Whoa, whoa.
Hold on a second. I got something.

32:06.592 --> 32:08.593
Check that out.

32:08.594 --> 32:10.762
So Fort Harmony was an Army hospital

32:10.763 --> 32:12.472
where Frederick Vought worked.

32:12.473 --> 32:14.724
The government designated it Top Secret

32:14.725 --> 32:16.477
and then decommissioned it after the war.

32:17.645 --> 32:19.520
Why is that square blurry?

32:19.521 --> 32:21.147
That's what
the military does to keep

32:21.148 --> 32:22.815
classified facilities hidden.

32:22.816 --> 32:24.692
Now, I'll bet you
a porterhouse at Luger's

32:24.693 --> 32:26.903
that's where Vought was testing the V1.

32:26.904 --> 32:29.322
If there's any more left out there,
that would be the fuckin' place to look.

32:29.323 --> 32:30.324
Hmm.

32:36.955 --> 32:38.498
-  Were you followed?
-  Hell no.

32:38.499 --> 32:40.750
Homelander's looking for V1,
just like we are.

32:40.751 --> 32:42.251
It was only a matter of time
before he found you.

32:42.252 --> 32:45.129
We're at 90 feet
below solid concrete.

32:45.130 --> 32:47.548
The door is
munitions grade ballistics resistant,

32:47.549 --> 32:49.801
same as the NORAD bunker
in Cheyenne Mountain.

32:49.802 --> 32:51.886
It will hold.

32:52.888 --> 32:54.972
Better hope so.

33:02.147 --> 33:03.481
Oh, thank fuck.

33:03.482 --> 33:04.857
Won't hold forever.

33:04.858 --> 33:07.194
So we're trapped down here.
What's the plan?

33:07.820 --> 33:09.278
Wait.

33:09.279 --> 33:10.614
Has anyone seen Zoe?

34:24.813 --> 34:26.398
Dad?

34:29.860 --> 34:31.862
- Zoe?
- Dad?

34:34.406 --> 34:35.908
Zoe...

34:37.117 --> 34:38.743
Oh, my God, Zoe.

34:41.246 --> 34:43.123
Oh, my God.

35:08.065 --> 35:10.274
Qu'est-ce que vous faites?!

35:10.275 --> 35:11.360
He told me Zoe was dead.

35:13.779 --> 35:15.739
And he's the one who killed Vicky,
not Homelander!

35:16.657 --> 35:19.159
Fucking psycho!
And you all went along with it.

35:22.996 --> 35:24.122
Come on, Zoe.

35:25.874 --> 35:27.292
I'm sorry, mon pote.

35:28.544 --> 35:30.169
I cannot allow you to leave.

35:32.339 --> 35:33.798
Please.

35:33.799 --> 35:35.843
Don't make me shoot your papa.

35:38.345 --> 35:39.388
No.

35:40.848 --> 35:42.974
- Let them go.
- She tried to kill us both.

35:42.975 --> 35:45.768
She should grow up like a kid.
Not like us.

35:50.315 --> 35:51.315
Go.

36:10.586 --> 36:12.545
Zoe, pick up.

36:12.546 --> 36:14.547
Listen to me. Do not come home

36:14.548 --> 36:15.840
until I tell you to.

36:15.841 --> 36:18.217
It's not safe, you understand? Call me.

36:18.218 --> 36:19.887
Do we know when she left?

36:23.056 --> 36:24.974
Through the service hatch
a few hours ago.

36:24.975 --> 36:26.393
Can we get out that way?

36:28.103 --> 36:31.022
That's precisely
where Noir is patrolling.

36:31.023 --> 36:32.733
Well,
if that's the case...

36:34.359 --> 36:35.777
...then what are you packin'?

36:38.196 --> 36:39.405
Whoa.

36:39.406 --> 36:41.325
I've been looking for those.

36:42.367 --> 36:44.786
- Hmm.
-  Ah...

36:46.496 --> 36:48.122
Oro Blanco.

36:49.124 --> 36:50.584
Five hundred a stick.

36:51.668 --> 36:52.544
Oh.

37:19.363 --> 37:22.699
You know, my father spent
his whole life fightin' Vought.

37:23.951 --> 37:27.996
And here I am, smokin'
a fuckin' cigar with Stan Edgar.

37:28.872 --> 37:31.083
I remember your father, you know.

37:32.876 --> 37:35.294
He was impressive.

37:35.295 --> 37:38.005
Over 30 Ivy League attorneys at Vought,

37:38.006 --> 37:40.883
and one small-time Harlem lawyer

37:40.884 --> 37:44.011
made them work weekends and holidays.

37:44.012 --> 37:46.347
